I found a concrete behavioral risk in the new path: `SyncBridge.connect()` hydrates full history through `SyncNode.fetchMessages()`, and that currently fires `onUserMessage` callbacks for every historical user message. On resumed sessions that can replay old prompts into the agent loop. I’m checking the runner code now so I can fix this without breaking legitimate resume behavior.
